INACTIVE ~ sleeping (but wont be woken!) : 
	f's won't be placed in the broad-phase
		 (won't participate in collisions, (dynamics?) ray casts, etc.)
  -can create a body in an inactive state (and later re-activate it (bodyDef.active = true))
 
  b.SetActive()
   
  b.IsActive() 
 
b.SetSleepingAllowed()

b.IsSleepingAllowed() 
b.SetAwake()
b.IsAwake() 


